Class BNO055IMU.Parameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qualcomm.hardware.bosch.BNO055IMU.Parameters

    BNO055IMU

    public static class BNO055IMU.Parameters
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Instances of Parameters contain data indicating how a BNO055 absolute orientation sensor is to be initialized.
    See Also:
    BNO055IMU.initialize(Parameters)
